{
  "3140620": {
    "name": "C.A.S.T. (CHERNOZEM ANOMALY STRIKE TEAM)",
    "steam_appid": 3140620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎新成员加入C.A.S.T.（黑土镇异常打击小队）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入一个架空的1950年代欧洲，在这款合作第三人称撤离射击游戏中迎接挑战。配备交缠着复古风格的先进科技装备，你的队伍将面对可怕的威胁与异常现象。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1cbff27ae68867fd3a0052d04a27b712.poster.avif?t=1752481894\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1cbff27ae68867fd3a0052d04a27b712.webm?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1cbff27ae68867fd3a0052d04a27b712.mp4?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/a6f53a0c9563a0174c0dea7825206340.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是单人游玩还是合作游玩（1-4名玩家），都能体验动态玩法，完成独特目标与富有挑战性的支线任务。精确的团队合作与策略是成功的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/964627260427f04ab22bc2ea472a7240.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭于精心打造的地图，这些地图融入了程序化元素与多变的天气条件。每张地图都设有独特目标和随机异常现象。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/432968bb573f2605d9d56f0413e50a2c.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备各种远程与近战武器，每种武器都有升级选项。利用独特的改装模组打造并优化你的装备，并在制作工坊中强化现有武器或打造新装备。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/fa030bf879f77b823d94cdb69a2ff68f.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎战各类敌人，每种敌人都有不同的战斗风格与战术。灵活调整策略，才能在它们的攻击下生存。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/d3ada455703fb618a99986fc8681efba.poster.avif?t=1752481894\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/d3ada455703fb618a99986fc8681efba.webm?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/d3ada455703fb618a99986fc8681efba.mp4?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
